10.body: At the heart of the Ethereum protocol and operation is the Ethereum Virtual Machine, or EVM for short. -- Andreas Antonopoulos EVM is the Lingua Franca of Smart Contracts -- Daniel Ferrin
10.breadcrumbs: Ethereum Virtual Machine (EVM) » Ethereum Virtual Machine (EVM)
10.title: Ethereum Virtual Machine (EVM)

11.body: 1.The Yellow Paper : Main Ethereum Specification. 2. Beige Paper : More digestable than the Yellow Paper. 3. Evm-Deep-Dives by Noxx : Great hands-on explanation of how the EVM works. 4. Wonderful series by OpenZeppelin : Part 1 Part 2 5. Deconstructing a Smart Contract Series by OpenZeppelin : Part 1 Part 2 Part 3 Part 4 Part 5 Part 6 6. Mastering Ethereum : The iconical Ethereum book by Andreas Antonopoulos. This a must read. 7.Eth Wiki : A comprehensive list of resources related to the EVM. 8. Stack Machine Fundamentals : Simple explanation about stack machines. 9. Stack Machine Fundamentals : Simple explanation about stack machines. 10. EVM Illustrated : Amazing illustration of the EVM in pdf format. 11. EVM Illustrated : Amazing illustration of the EVM in pdf format. 12. Diving into Ethereum's World State : Blog post written by Timothy McCallum, explaining Ethereum's world state. 13. From Solidity to Bytecode, Memory and Storage : Great Hands-On video by the Ethereum Engineering Group. 14. Reverse Engineering a Contract : Understand a contract by having just the bytecode (NO SOURCE!). 15. Understanding Storage : Simple and easy to grasp explanation on how Ethereum's storage works. 16. Bytecode and Opcode Basics : Blog post written by Bernard Peh, explaining the basics of bytecode and opcode. 17. Opcodes Playground : Opcodes Playground. 18. The Ethereum Virtual Machine - Solidity Docs : Explanation of the EVM in the Solidity docs.
